Title: Meet Market
Plot: Nick and Keppler investigate the bizarre world of the black market sales of body parts after they find a body that has been burned and the organs removed.  The rest of the CSI team investigates the death of rich woman who was killed in her own home.
GuestStars: Kayla Mae Maloney, Douglas Sills, Michael Weaver, Tymberlee Chanel, Ivan Shawn, Jason Olive, Joy Bisco, Jo Anderson, Robin Thomas, John Toles-Bey, John Hensley, Gordon Clapp, Liev Schreiber
